{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21142.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"Her wish...","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"At first she just looked sad when she told@me about it, but by the time she was done,@her expression was clearly pained."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Rika","nameRight":"Ren","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"I'm a disgusting human being, aren't I?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101}],"textLeft":"You must really hate me now..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302501}],"textRight":"Huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"You might've thought I'm nice because@I said I'd listen to what's bothering you..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101}],"textLeft":"But now you see the truth...@This is who I really am..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"textRight":"...I don't hate you..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501}],"textRight":"You...feel bad...about what you did..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302501}],"textRight":"...No...I'm sure...@You're...a good person..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"textRight":"And so...no...@I don't hate you!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Haha, I'm glad..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101}],"textLeft":"I'd be seriously bummed if you did..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"I'm really, really glad..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"Maybe it was because she was relieved,@but for a minute...@I thought she was going to cry.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21142.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"That's my dark confession."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…@[chara:302501:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:302501:lipSynch_1]Why…?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"Why did I tell you my story all of a sudden?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Yeah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Well, I mean, it's not fair, is it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Not...fair?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Just asking you to do all the talking..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303101}],"textLeft":"It's not fair, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"I figure if I want you to open your heart@to me, first I need to open my own."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101}],"textLeft":"The only thing I could think of to do was to@tell you my own secret..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Do you feel like talking at all?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101}],"textLeft":"Do you feel like we've gotten a little@closer now?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"textRight":"(She did that...for me...)","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"Even though it was painful for her to talk@about, she told me her story so I wouldn't@feel so much distance between us.@I was so happy...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21142.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnEffect":"stop"},{"narration":"That's when I decided I wanted to tell@her what was inside my heart too..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Umm... I...@You see, I..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Yeah...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501}],"textRight":"I…@[chara:302501:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:302501:motion_200][chara:302501:cheek_1][chara:302501:face_mtn_ex_020.exp.json][chara:302501:lipSynch_1]I...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"I want to talk...@I want to tell her!@But I still…","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21142.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Ummm..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302501,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"(I want to talk, but I can't!)","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Ren","narration":"Why am I like this?@Why can't I speak?","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21142.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302501,"motion":300,"tear":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Uh...uh...uhhh...@*Sniffle* *Sob*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303101,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Oh! Ren?!@[chara:303101:lipSynch_0][wait:0.5][chara:303101:motion_400][chara:303101:lipSynch_1]"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":2}